DeJw">Thiệu Trị hoàng đế</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-H%C3%BAc/S%C6%A1n-th%C3%B4n-khi%E1%BB%83n-ho%C3%A0i/poem-qk2VsGhuocApaZN_AMyBcw">Sơn thôn khiển hoài - 山村遣懷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-H%C3%BAc/author-udskGfyCijQjK6PP08MOjw">Nguyễn Húc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/Thu-d%E1%BA%A1-l%E1%BB%AF-%C4%91%C3%ACnh/poem-keynlfmxw1p_9dJNv4HaGg">Thu dạ lữ đình - 秋夜旅亭</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-giang-chu-th%E1%BB%A9/poem-nv76_bEgDF_AyZ3rSnDHQQ">Tương giang chu thứ - 湘江舟次</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ph%C3%BA-L%E1%BB%99c-b%C3%A1t-c%E1%BA%A3nh-k%E1%BB%B3-6-Linh-Th%C3%A1i/poem-Y6cxMFq5zXo0K9M-XGtWIg">Vịnh Phú Lộc bát cảnh kỳ 6 - Linh Thái - 詠富祿八景其六－靈蔡</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/author-DYGad0thHvgCxK3Szp1zVQ">Trần Đình Túc</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
